data.description: This patio home is located on a quiet cul de sac on the desirable West side. It has been meticulously cared for and is move in ready. Roomy kitchen with pantry, lots of cabinets and dining area, large combo living/dining area, 2 bedrooms, with additional walk out room for office or small den. The Master bedroom is spacious and has 2 closets. One is a walk-in closet with built-ins and attic storage access and the other is a double closet with shelves for linens. The master bath has a double vanity, free standing shower, separate toilet room. The second bedroom has 2 double closets. There is a built-in workbench in the garage. This is a quiet and well maintained area.
